							<article class="postItem post--list--simple clearfix post-8134 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-covid-19-and-the-social-sciences category-covid-19-fieldnotes">
	<a href="https://items.ssrc.org/category/covid-19-and-the-social-sciences/covid-19-fieldnotes/" title="View all posts in Covid-19 Fieldnotes from Our Grantees" rel="tag" class="postCategory">Covid-19 Fieldnotes from Our Grantees</a>	<h3 class="postTitle entry-title">
		<a href="https://items.ssrc.org/covid-19-and-the-social-sciences/covid-19-fieldnotes/were-indigenous-peoples-vulnerable-or-resilient-strategies-to-cope-with-covid-19-in-the-peruvian-amazon-basin/" rel="bookmark">Were Indigenous Peoples’ Vulnerable or Resilient? Strategies to Cope with Covid-19 in the Peruvian Amazon Basin</a>
	</h3>
			<div class="postMeta--author postMeta--author--1 o-media vcard author">
			<div class="postMeta--author-avatar o-media-left o-media--middle photo"><img width="72" height="72" src="https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-96x96.png" class="avatar avatar-72 photo wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-48x48@2x.png 96w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-150x150@2x.png 300w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-150x150.png 150w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-400x400.png 400w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-100x100.png 100w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-24x24.png 24w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-24x24@2x.png 48w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square.png 426w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-96x96@2x.png 192w, https://mk0itemsssrcorgqb419.kinstacdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/delgado-square-100x100@2x.png 200w" sizes="(max-width: 72px) 100vw, 72px" /></div>
			<div class="postMeta--author-text o-media-body o-media--middle">
				<span class="postMeta--author-author metaFont fn"><a href="https://items.ssrc.org/author/deborah-delgado-pugley/" title="Posts by Deborah Delgado Pugley" class="url fn" rel="author">Deborah Delgado Pugley</a></span><span class="middot">&middot;</span>
